// text menu
// also shows composing replies with {@trigger}

! local concat = newline

> topic menu inherits global_commands

    + start
    - Choose a size:
    ^ 1) Small
    ^ 2) Medium
    ^ 3) Large

    + (1|s|small)
    - itsy bitsy {@deliver}

    + (2|m|medium)
    - middling {@deliver}

    + (3|L|large)
    - yuuuge! {@deliver}

    + deliver
    - coming your way!
    - coming over!
    - as you like!

< topic
